  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Add Continuous Crank FB</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" style="page-break-before:always;">Why should I use a Continuous-Crank FB?</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">In a Cam mechanism, you usually design the motion for a Tool-Part and <text styleclass="VariableName">MechDesigner</text> calculates the motion of the Follower-Part with with Inverse-Kinematics. Typically the Follower-Part oscillates through an angle that is less than 180º, and usually less than 90º.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">It also possible with Servo mechanisms to design the motion of a Tool-Part, but you want the motion of the Part that you drive with a rotating servo-motor to rotate by 180º, and even continually rotate.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">A typical application of the <text styleclass="Element">Continuous-Crank FB</text> is to find the correct length and rotational motion of a Crank to give the motion you design and want for a Tool-Part.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See also: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-FunctionBlock-ContinuousCrank">Continuous-Crank FB dialog</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Add Continuous Crank FB</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;&#32;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="false" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Add a Continuous-Crank FB to the graphics-area </li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="2" colcount="2">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="width:40px; border-top:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;">
